<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-53-0423 </DOCNO><TEXT>Computer security is a growing concern in research, development, marketing,and most other areas of everyday life. The first and foremost task incomputer security is to prevent unauthorized access to systems. Thisreport tells how ``crackers'' (computer wizards who use their talentsfor illegal and destructive purposes) obtain access to computer systemsand gives specific advice on how to prevent them from doing it. 11 refs.,5 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>